title: 18 Minimal Techno Sets - DJ Max Portland
description:
These 18 sets will take you on a journey of the last 2.5 years of my life. Each set is based on specific events in my life. The names represent exactly that. My sets are never pre-planned. EXCEPT: The NINTENDO TRIBUTE SETS:) Those sets have a video that follows the set. Other than that my sets are never planned and come only from within.


Nintendo Tributes and Bassment Adventures sets can be seen here
